Module wgu.dansmithc195project
Package wgu.dansmithc195project.controllers

Class AppointmentFormController

java.lang.Object
wgu.dansmithc195project.controllers.AppointmentFormController
public class AppointmentFormController extends Object
This controller is a form to add appointments to the database. The appointment ID will be autogenerated, the user adds the Title, Location, Type, and Description as necessary, then chooses a contact, customer, and user from the corresponding dropdown menus, then chooses a start date & time and end date & time.
